title: Check Out Our New League Youtube Channel!! My Fellow Leaguers!! -GroupOfNerds
body:
My friends and I started a LoL youtube channel early this year we play and record our games for the fun and laughs, head on over and see if you like our content! I enjoy making these so im trying to get the name out to see what the peoples reaction is. Tell me what you think!! Cheers guys!! :D
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1GrjX3G-1Kq1_lf3SOOnaw
